Netschi Gets 8 Years, 4 Months in Prison for $80 Million ATM Ponzi Scheme

-- B y   D a v i d   V o r e a c o s
-- 
2011-04-22T20:54:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-22/netschi-gets-8-years-4-months-in-prison-for-80-million-atm-ponzi-scheme.html
Walter Netschi, convicted of
running an $80 million Ponzi scheme based on phony investments
in automated teller machines, was sentenced to eight years and
four months in prison.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Voreacos in Newark at 
 dvoreacos@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Hytha at 
 mhytha@bloomberg.net  